title: 2021 Trade Deadline & TNF Preview
itunes:title: 2021 Trade Deadline & TNF Preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Colleen Wolfe bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including the trade deadline and moves around the league. The heroes recap the MNF game and also preview the TNF matchup between the Jets and the Colts - Dan and Marc's favorite teams.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
